  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Toplana Zenica GET Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Bank will provide a long term senior loan of EUR 41 million to joint  venture Toplana Zenica d.o.o. for the construction of a new Combined Heat &amp;amp;amp;  Power Plant (CHP). The project will transfer the production of steam and blast  air for ArcelorMittal Zenica&apos;s steelworks and the production of district  heating water for the City of Zenica, from currently ArcelorMittal Zenica to a  modern CHP owned by the Borrower. The Project will entail the replacement of  all outdated, coal-based steam generators with modern units fully using  recovery gases from the steelworks and natural gas (as back up).</narrative>
  </description>
